Two Negroes were admitted,

206
00:22:40,344 --> 00:22:43,263
but only after Governor George
Wallace had carried out

207
00:22:43,388 --> 00:22:46,642
his symbolic threat
to stand in the schoolhouse door.

208
00:22:49,519 --> 00:22:51,438
Earl, what's going on?

209
00:22:51,563 --> 00:22:54,024
Coons are trying to get into school.

210
00:22:54,149 --> 00:22:57,027
Coons? When racoons
tried getting on our back porch,

211
00:22:57,152 --> 00:22:59,446
Mama just chased them off
with a broom.

212
00:22:59,571 --> 00:23:04,409
Not racoons, you idiot. Niggers.
They want to go to school with us.

213
00:23:04,534 --> 00:23:06,453
With us? They do?

214
00:23:06,578 --> 00:23:08,455
Shortly after Governor Wallace

215
00:23:08,580 --> 00:23:11,416
had carried out his promise
to block the doorway,

216
